1951;;Francis Goes to the Races;;American;;Arthur Lubin;;Donald O'Connor, Piper Laurie;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Francis_Goes_to_the_Races;;Francis the Talking Mule and his sidekick Peter Sterling visit Colonel Travers and his granddaughter on their family horse farm. Peter soon finds himself involved in the world of horse racing and a crime boss and his men trying to "fix" races involving the Travers' horses.